{"tid":631073,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"老 公 Sergio 做 湊 女 公  梁 詠 琪 安 心 傾 偈","createTime":"2018-04-16T06:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T06:51:05.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"22811ae7ec85ab07f402dee12337e4f9dfd6965e","tid":631073,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:45:50.000Z","msg":"梁詠琪（GiGi）下個月會喺紅館舉行演唱會，趁未進入倒階段，GiGi都盡量抽時間陪家人，《蘋果》讀者李小姐，日前就喺數碼港巧遇GiGi一家，並透過「爆相爆片」分享當日拍下GiGi和西班牙籍丈夫Sergio及女兒Sofia嘅相片。<br />\n<br />\n李小姐表示：「嗰日見到GiGi時大約4點左右，佢同老公、囡囡，仲有傅家俊一家，見到大部份時間都係佢老公照顧個女，又抱又餵囡囡食香蕉。」問李小姐可有其他人發現GiGi一家？佢話：「有呀，都有人搵佢影相，不過佢都有禮貌咁推咗，聽到佢話因為嗰日係同屋企人去玩，所以唔影相，之後啲人就叫傅家俊影。」<br />\n<br />\n當日數碼港搞嘉年華，現場有唔少小朋友啱玩嘅機動遊戲，李小姐見到GiGi嘅時候，佢就同老公等人陪Sofia排隊玩碰碰車。李小姐仲話佢哋之前都有玩啲攤位遊戲，但唔見有贏禮物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180411/large/1523437800_4461.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180411%2Flarge%2F1523437800_4461.jpg&h=226736ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180411/large/1523437802_67d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180411%2Flarge%2F1523437802_67d3.jpg&h=efe1efeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180411/large/1523438148_1c42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180411%2Flarge%2F1523438148_1c42.jpg&h=13b604da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180411/large/1523438149_3f82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180411%2Flarge%2F1523438149_3f82.jpg&h=96515cce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1650e3347a8a2f3ee0bddfc526e83e7bfae401f4","tid":631073,"uid":11254,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:46:37.000Z","msg":"西班牙"},{"pid":"054cbbb55cfa1e429f3aa1f26da8f28069eb6a38","tid":631073,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:47:41.000Z","msg":"垃圾樓豬，你除左貼埋d垃圾新聞仲有咩人生意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4211c85c5e78bab4683474c96681c1c5f0609653","tid":631073,"uid":46042,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:51:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/16/145104_dff793873314aa272530fe205cf76d74.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F16%2F145104_dff793873314aa272530fe205cf76d74.png&h=e20a6971&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}